Mai ba da rahoto na Lakers, Mike Trudell ya wallafa cewa James zai yi wasa ne kawai na iyakantaccen lokaci.
Bayan horo a farkon makon nan, an tambayi James game da jadawalin wasanni shida na Lakers na kakar wasa ta gaba.
