Wannan shi ne babban abin da ya faru a lokacin taron Trump a West Virginia.
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara taron zaɓe a garin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia a daren yau.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin taron da aka shirya a wurare biyar a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da wurare masu kyau ga Trump kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
A yanzu da ake jiran zaben tabbatar da nadin babban alkalin kotun, Trump na neman karfafa goyon baya a zaben da ake shirin yi a watan Nuwamba, saboda jam'iyyar Republican na fuskantar barazanar rasa rinjaye a majalisar dokoki.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a yammacin Virginia zai gudana kuma ta yaya zan iya kallon sa a yanar gizo?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, a ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018 da karfe 7 na yamma.
Za a iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kan layi ta hanyar YouTube:
A yayin da FBI ke binciken zargin cin zarafin dan takarar kotun kolin Amurka Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ake zargi da cin zarafinsa, Trump zai yi magana game da sauraron karar Kavanaugh a wannan makon, yayin da kuri'ar amincewa da zaben majalisar dattijai ta jinkirta har zuwa mako guda.
Amma babban manufar wannan taro da ake ci gaba da yi shi ne karfafa karfin jam'iyyar Republican a lokacin da take fuskantar kalubale a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A cewar Reuters, saboda haka, jam'iyyar Trump ta ce taron biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, za su yi ne don "karfafa masu sa kai da masu goyon baya don karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye na jam'iyyar Republican a majalisar dattijai da majalisar wakilai".
"Gaskiya ne cewa samun rinjaye a majalisar wakilai yana da matukar muhimmanci ga manufofinsa, don haka shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da dama a lokacin zabe mai cike da aiki", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump da ya nemi a sakaya sunansa.
A cewar Metro News na West Virginia, taron da aka shirya a daren yau a West Bank Arena a Wheeling "na iya tara magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma za a buga shi a kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh".
Trump ya lashe zaben da kashi 40 cikin dari a jihar West Virginia a shekarar 2016, amma ziyarar da ya kai a ranar Asabar ita ce ziyarar Trump ta biyu a cikin wata guda.
Trump yana son tallafawa dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ke baya a zaben.
A cewar Reuters, Simon Heder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, ya ce "ba kyakkyawan alama ba ne ga Morrissey cewa shugaban ya zo don ya tallafa masa".
