A halin yanzu, waɗannan 'yan wasan suna da wasa ɗaya kawai a kowace wasa.
Za a ci nasara a rami 18.
A cikin kwanaki biyu da suka gabata, 'yan wasan da suka samu karin maki fiye da Spears da Thomas sune kawai Francesco Morinari da Tommy Fleetwood, wadanda suka kasance mafi yawan maganganun gasar Ryder Cup.
Waɗannan mutane biyu da aka zaɓa a Turai, ba su da kuskure kuma sun ci nasara a cikin gwagwarmaya huɗu.
Ba wai kawai su ne kawai ma'aurata da ake kira "Mollywood" ba su buga wasan bogey a ranar Asabar da yamma ba, amma sun guje wa wasan bogey a ranar Asabar da safe, Jumma'a da yamma, da kuma ƙarshen ƙarfe tara na ranar Jumma'a.
Bayan wannan wasan, idan aka dubi yadda waɗannan 'yan wasa biyu ke da kuzari a cikin taron jama'a, to, za a iya cewa su ne' yan wasan da za su yi nasara a ranar Lahadi. Kuma babu wani ɗan wasa da ya fi Fleetwood da Morinari shahara don kada ya rinjayi gasar zakarun Turai a gasar Le Golf National.
Kuma ina so su biyu su cimma hakan a lokaci guda a wani zaure daban.
Duk da haka, har yanzu ba a yanke shawarar nasarar zaben Turai ba.
Babba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi nasara da Sergio Garcia da Alex Nolen, jaruman da suka yi nasara a wannan safiya.
