Fowler da Forsom suna da ban sha'awa sosai a kusa da su saboda hulɗar da ke tsakanin su, shawarwari da ba su ba, da kuma canjin canjin dabarun lokaci.
Ko da yake, a wannan karon, 'yan wasan Turai sun fi kyau a matsayin ƙungiya, suna da babban jagoranci a ranar ƙarshe, amma a wannan taron, an nuna cewa 'yan wasan Amurka suna son yin gwagwarmaya don kawar da damuwa, musamman ma a gefen Amurka.
A ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder, gasar cin kofin Turai ta ci gaba da ci 10-6.
Ƙungiyar Turai ta ci gaba da kasancewa a gaban Amurka da 10-6 bayan wasan da suka yi a ranar Asabar a Fowl da Forsum, kuma suna ci gaba da tafiya zuwa ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup.
Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Morinari sun yi nasara sau biyu a kan Tiger Woods, wanda ke fama da fama, kuma sun kara maki hudu a gasar Le Golf National.
Zaɓen Turai na Thomas Bion, wanda ke neman dawo da kyautar da ya rasa a Hazeltin shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ya mamaye zaɓen Amurka mai wahala a cikin wasan safe, ya sa ci ya zama 3-1.
Ƙasar Amurka ta sake dawowa a Forsum kuma ta lashe wasanni biyu, amma har yanzu ba ta iya kawar da bambanci ba.
Jim Furyk ya jagoranci Amurka, yana buƙatar samun maki takwas a wasannin 12 na ranar Lahadi don riƙe da kyautar.
Fritwood ba kawai ta zama farkon rookie na Turai da ya ci maki huɗu a jere ba, amma ma'aurata biyu da suka ci maki huɗu a wasannin farko na gasar Ryder Cup, wanda aka kira "Mollywood" bayan ƙarshen mako mai ban sha'awa.
Bayan sun kayar da Woods da Patrick Reed a kwallon gaba, sun nuna kyakkyawar hadin kai, kuma sun ci nasara da ci 5 da 4, wanda ya fi fice a cikin Woods da rookie Bryson Deschambore.
Woods wanda bai yi nasara ba a wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna kyakkyawan wasa a wasu lokuta, amma ba wai kawai ya rasa wasanni 19 daga cikin 29 a Fowler da Forsum ba, amma har ma ya sha wahala a wasanni bakwai.
Bayan ya huta a wasan kwallon kafa na safe, Justin Rose ya yi wasa da Henrik Stenson a Forsum, inda ya doke Dustin Johnson da Brooks Keppka, na farko da na uku a duniya, 2 da 1 .
Ko da yake hanyar da ke kudu maso yammacin Paris ta zama rana mai kyau don jin daɗin iska mai iska, amma zaɓin Turai bai mallaki yadda ya kamata ba.
Jordan Spies da Justin Thomas, wadanda suka lashe manyan wasanni uku, sun nuna matsayin da za a bi a zabar Amurka.
Bayan sun yi nasara da John Ram da Ian Polter na Spain da 2 da 1 a wasan kwallon kafa, sun ci nasara da Polter da Rory McIlroy da 4 da 3 yayin da suka rasa ramuka biyu na farko a Forsum.
A tarihin gasar Ryder Cup, akwai lokuta biyu kawai da aka sake juyawa daga maki hudu a cikin singles, amma Amurka ta jagoranci Furik ta iya riƙe kyautar kawai ta hanyar kawowa.
Amma ga 'yan takarar Amurka da suka yi kwana biyu a kasa, harin na ranar Lahadi ya fi karfin su.
A lokacin da aka yi wannan magana, sai na ji cewa, "Babu wani abu da zai sa a yi wannan magana".
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa, tsauraran takunkumi da ake yi wa kasar sun kara tsanantawa da rashin amincewa da Amurka, kuma ba za ta yi watsi da makaman nukiliyar ta hanyar daya ba.
Ministan harkokin wajen kasar Li Yongho ya shaida wa babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa kasar ta Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "manyan matakai na alheri" a cikin shekara guda da ta gabata, ciki har da dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da makaman rokoki, rushe wuraren gwajin makaman nukiliya da kuma yin alkawarin hana yaduwar makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya.
"Amma ba mu ga amsar da ta dace daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
"Idan ba za mu amince da Amurka ba, za mu rasa amincewa da tsaron kasa, kuma a karkashin irin wannan yanayi ba za mu iya kawar da makamanmu ba".
Ministan harkokin wajen kasar Lee ya sake maimaita sanannen rashin jin dadin da Arewa ta yi game da rashin samun sakamako daga gwamnatin Amurka kan tsarin "mataki-mataki" na kawar da nukiliya, amma sanarwa da ya yi tana da ma'ana saboda, sabanin da ya gabata, gwamnatin ta Arewa ba ta yi watsi da yunkurin kawar da nukiliya ba.
A taron farko da ya yi da shugaban Amurka da shugabannin Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga watan Yuni, Li ya yi alkawarin cewa Kim Jong Un zai yi aiki kan "kawar da nukiliya daga yankin Koriya ta Kudu" kuma ya ambaci sanarwar hadin gwiwa da Trump ya yi game da tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa na son kawo karshen yakin Koriya a shekarar 1950 zuwa 1953, amma Amurka ta ce Koriya ta Arewa dole ne ta fara watsi da makaman nukiliya.
Gwamnatin Amurka ta kuma yi tsayayya da kiran da ake yi na sassauta tsauraran takunkumin da kasashen duniya suka kakaba wa Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta yi ikirarin 'ba da nukiliya a farko' kuma ta matsa lamba ta hanyar takunkumi don cimma burinta ta hanyar tilasta shi, kuma tana adawa da sanarwar dakatar da yaki", in ji Li.
"Gaskiyar cewa takunkumi zai iya cinye mu shine mafarkin mutanen da basu san mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce, ci gaba da takunkumi ya kara mana rashin yarda".
Ministan harkokin wajen kasar ya ce ba zai tattauna batun taron shugabannin kasashen biyu ba, kamar yadda shugaba Trump ya bayyana a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon nan.
Maimakon haka, ya jaddada ganawarsa da Shugaba Kim Jong-un na Koriya ta Kudu sau uku a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata, ya kara da cewa: "Idan Koriya ta Kudu ce ta fara batun nukiliya maimakon Amurka, to, ba za a sami wannan matsalar ba".
Ko da yake, sautin jawabin na Li ya bambanta sosai da lokacin da Gold ya kira Trump "muguwar shugaba" da kuma lokacin da Trump ya kira Gold "mutumin rokoki" a kan harin kunar bakin wake, bayan ya ce rokoki daga Koriya ta Arewa ba za su iya kaiwa Amurka ba a taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a bara.
A shekarar da ta gabata, Trump ya yi barazanar "hallaka" Koriya ta Arewa, amma ya yaba wa Gold a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a wannan shekara saboda ƙarfin hali da ya nuna wajen kawar da makaman, amma ya ce akwai matsaloli da yawa da za a fuskanta kuma dole ne a ci gaba da sanya takunkumi har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta kawar da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce, "Babu matsala, zai ɗauki shekaru biyu, uku ko watanni biyar".
Kasashen Sin da Rasha sun ce bai kamata Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta dauki matakin da Koriya ta Arewa ta dauka ba.
Amma sakataren harkokin wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya fada a majalisar tsaron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Alhamis cewa: "Ya kamata a ci gaba da tsaurara takunkumin da majalisar ta sanya a kan kasar har sai an tabbatar da cewa an kammala kuma an kawar da makaman nukiliya".
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kara tsaurara takunkumi kan kasar ta Arewa tun shekara ta 2006 domin dakile kudaden da take bayarwa wajen bunkasa makaman nukiliya da na makaman nukiliya.
Pompeo ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe domin shirya taron shugabannin biyu.
A wannan shekarar, Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku, amma ziyarar da ya yi a baya ba ta kawo nasara ba.
